  "description": "<p><strong>World No.1 player in industry is hiring Operator</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>・Following health and safety standards.</p><p>・Maintaining a clean workstation</p><p>・Following production guidelines and specifications.</p><p>・Operating and maintaining machinery or production line equipment.</p><p>・Monitoring the assembly line and removing faulty products.</p><p>・Working on the production line and meeting production targets.</p><p>・Reporting any issues to the superior.</p><p>・Performing other tasks as assigned.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Able to commit to OT if required</li><li>Committed to routine and repetitive job </li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Other information</strong></p><ul><li>Location : West</li><li>Company coach available from Jurong East MRT</li><li>Working Hrs : 8:30AM – 5:30PM Off on Sat & Sun</li><li>Free Lunch and uniform including safety gear are provided.</li><li>Medical and dental benefit is provided.</li><li>Opportunity to convert from term employment to permanent employment. </li></ul>",
